snippet.title: Active Neurons 3 - Wonders Of The World - Launch Trailer | PS5, PS4
snippet.description:
A puzzle that trains spatial and logical thinking. Power up your brains!
In the game, you have to follow 3 simple steps:
1) Collect energy
2) Charge your brain
3) Explore Wonders of the World
But are these steps that easy? Try it yourself and you will find out everything!
